  "description": "A complete Bootstrap app with built-in features like routing, page rendering and basic SEO.",
  "summary": "Use this dossier when building a Next.js App Router site whose pages, SEO metadata, and media URLs are sourced from Glide Publishing Platform APIs. It provides the core Glide fetch/config layer, a catch-all page pattern for CMS-driven routing, optional static path generation, and a middleware pattern for noindexing non-production environments.",
